Angelo De Garo v. Antoinette Marino et al.

Motion granted insofar as to dispense with printing of the exhibits enumerated in the moving affidavit of Edward S. Marshall, on condition that the originals thereof shall be filed with this court on or before the Wednesday preceding the first day of the term for which the appeal is noticed for argument. Concur • — • Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Valente and Stevens, JJ.
